quran[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif Laam Raa 67. Iyo ni imirongo (ayat) y’igitabo, ikaba (n’imirongo ya) Qur’an isobanutse"
  15,2,(Ku munsi w’imperuka) babandi bahakanye bazicuza impamvu batabaye Abayisilamu (igihe bazaba babona Abayisilamu bajyanwa mu ijuru naho abahakanyi bajyanwa mu muriro)
  15,3,"Bareke barye baninezeze, banarangazwe n’icyizere (cyo kuzaramba), vuba aha bazamenya (ko ibyiringiro byabo bitari ukuri)"
  15,4,"Nta mudugudu numwe twarimbuye, uretse ko wabaga ufite igihe cyawo cyagenwe"
  15,5,Nta muryango (umat) numwe ushobora (kurimburwa) mbere cyangwa nyuma y’igihe cyagenwe
  15,6,"Baranavuze bati \"Yewe uwahishuriwe urwibutso! Mu by’ukuri, wowe uri umusazi"
  15,7,Kuki utatuzanira abamalayika (bahamya ko uri intumwa ya Allah) niba koko uri umwe mu banyakuri
  15,8,"(Allah aravuga ati) \"Ntabwo twohereza abamalayika bitari mu kuri (iyo bazanye ibihano). Kandi icyo gihe (abahakanyi) ntibarindirizwa"
  15,9,"Mu by’ukuri, ni twe twahishuye urwibutso (Qur’an), kandi rwose ni na twetuzarurinda"
  15,10,"Mu by’ukuri, twohereje (intumwa) mbere yawe, mu matsinda y’ababayeho mbere"
  15,11,Kandi nta ntumwayabageragaho ngo babure kuyinnyega
  15,12,Uko ni ko dushyira (uwo muco wo kunnyega) mu mitima y’inkozizibibi (zo mu gihe cyawe)
  15,13,"Ntabwo bashobora kuyemera (Qur’an), kandi ingero (z’ibihano bya Allah) ku babayeho mbere zarabagezeho"
  15,14,"Kandi n’iyo tuza kubakingurira umuryango mu kirere, bagakomeza bazamuka (kugera ubwo babonye abamalayika, ntibari kwemera)"
  15,15,"Ahubwo bari kuvuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, amaso yacu yahumye. Ahubwo twe turi abantu barozwe"
  15,16,Kandi rwose twashyize inyenyeri nini mu kirere tunagitakira (abantu) bareba (kugira ngo babikuremo inyigisho)
  15,17,Twanakirinze amashitani yavumwe (kugira ngo atakigeramo akabasha kumviriza ibivugirwa mu ijuru)
  15,18,"Uretse amwe muri yo (amashitani) ashobora kugira ibyo yumviriza (bibera mu ijuru), maze agakurikizwa ibishashi by’umuriro bigaragara"
  15,19,"Twanarambuye isi maze tuyishyiraho imisozi yo kuyishimangira, tunayimezamo ibimera byose ku gipimo gikwiye"
  15,20,Twanayibashyiriyemo ibibabeshaho ndetse (n’ibibeshaho ibindi biremwa) mwe mudaha amafunguro
  15,21,"Kandi nta kintu na kimwe tudatunze mu bigega byacu, ndetse tubitanga ku rugero rukwiye"
  15,22,"Tunohereza imiyaga iremereza igicu, nuko tukamanura amazi aturutse mu kirere, tukayabaha ngo muyanywe; kandi ntabwo ari mwe mugenga ibigega byayo"
  15,23,"Mu by’ukuri, ni twe dutanga ubuzima n’urupfu, kandi ni twe bazungura (b’isi n’ibiyirimo)"
  15,24,"Rwose tuzi ababayeho mbere muri mwe, kandi rwose tuzi n’abazabaho nyuma"
  15,25,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe ni we uzabakoranya (ku munsi w’ibarura). Rwose ni we Ushishoza, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  15,26,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu (Adamu) mu ibumba ryumye ukomangaho rikirangira, mu cyondo cy’umukara cyahinduye ibara n’impumuro (kubera igihe cyari kimaze)"
  15,27,Naho Shitani tuyirema mbere (ya Adamu) tuyikomoye mu bishashi by’umuriro utagira umwotsi
  15,28,"Unibuke ubwo Nyagasani wawe yabwiraga Abamalayika ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ngiye kurema umuntu (Adamu) mu ibumba ryumye ukomangaho rikirangira, mu cyondo cy’umukara cyahinduye ibara n’impumuro (kubera igihe cyari kimaze)"
  15,29,"Nimara kumutunganya nkamuhuhamo roho inturutseho, muhite muca bugufi mumwubamire (byo kumuha icyubahiro atari ukumusenga)"
  15,30,Nuko Abamalayika bose barubama
  15,31,Uretse Ibilisi (Shitani) wanze kuba mu bubama
  15,32,"(Allah) aravuga ati \"Yewe Ibilisi! Kuki utubamye hamwe n’abubama"
  15,33,"(Ibilisi) aravuga ati \"Sinakubamira umuntu waremye mu ibumba ryumye ukomangaho rikirangira, mu cyondo cy’umukara cyahinduye ibara n’impumuro (kubera igihe cyari kimaze)"
  15,34,"(Allah) aravuga ati \"Ngaho sohoka hano (mu ijuru), kuko mu by’ukuri, ubaye ikivume"
  15,35,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, umuvumo wanjye uzakubaho kuzageza ku munsi w’imperuka"
  15,36,"(Ibilisi) aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Mpa kubaho kuzageza ku munsi (abapfuye) bazazurirwaho"
  15,37,"(Allah) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ubaye mu bazarindirizwa"
  15,38,Kuzageza ku munsi w’igihe kizwi
  15,39,"(Ibilisi) aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Kubera ko wampanishije kuyoba, rwose nzabakundisha inzira igana mu buyobe ku isi,nanabayobye bose"
  15,40,Uretse abagaragu bawe b’indobanure muri bo
  15,41,"(Allah) aravuga ati \"Iyi ni inzira igororotse igana iwanjye"
  15,42,"Mu by’ukuri, wowe nta bubasha uzagira ku bagaragu banjye, uretse abayobye bazagukurikira"
  15,43,"Kandi rwose, umuriro wa Jahanamu ni wobose basezeranyijwe"
  15,44,"Ufite imiryango irindwi, kandi buri muryango ufite (abanyabyaha) wagenewe"
  15,45,"Mu by’ukuri,abatinya Allah bazaba bari mu busitani (Ijuru) butembamo imigezi"
  15,46,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimuryinjiremo mu mahoro kandi mutekanye"
  15,47,"Tuzanakura inzika mu bituza byabo (nuko babane mu ijuru) nk’abavandimwe, bari ku bitanda berekeranye (baganira bishimye)"
  15,48,Ntibazigera barigiramo umunaniro kandi ntibazarivanwamo
  15,49,"(Yewe Muhamadi) bwira abagaragu banjye ko mu by’ukuri, ndi Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  15,50,Kandi ko n’ibihano byanjye ari ibihano bibabaza cyane
  15,51,Unababarire inkuru y’abashyitsi (abamalayika) ba Aburahamu
  15,52,"Ubwo binjiraga iwe bakavuga bati \"Salamu (amahoro)\" , (nuko akabikiriza) maze akavuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, muduteye ubwoba"
  15,53,"Baravuga bati \"Ntugire ubwoba! Mu by’ukuri, tuje kuguha inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara) umuhungu w’umunyabwenge"
  15,54,"(Aburahamu) aravuga ati \"Ese murampa inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara umuhungu) kandi ngeze mu zabukuru? Iyo nkuru nziza ni bwoko ki"
  15,55,"Baravuga bati \"Tuguhaye inkuru nziza y’ukuri. Bityo, reka kuba mu bihebye"
  15,56,"(Aburahamu) aravuga ati \"Nonese ni nde wakwiheba mu mpuhwe za Nyagasani we, usibye abayobye"
  15,57,"(Aburahamu arongera) aravuga ati \"Ni iki kibagenza yemwe mwa ntumwa mwe"
  15,58,"Baravuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, twoherejwe ku bantu b’inkozi z’ibibi (ngo tubarimbure)"
  15,59,"Usibye gusa umuryango wa Lutwi (Loti). Mu by’ukuri, turabarokora bose"
  15,60,Uretse umugore we (wigometse) twagennye ko aba mu bazasigara inyuma (bakarimbuka)
  15,61,Ubwo za ntumwa (abamalayika) zageraga ku muryango wa Lutwi (Loti)
  15,62,"(Loti) yaravuze ati \"Mu by’ukuri, sinabamenye"
  15,63,"Baravuga bati \"Ahubwo tukuzaniye ibyo bajyaga bashidikanyaho (ibihano)"
  15,64,"Tunakuzaniye ukuri (inkuru yo kurimbura inkozi z’ibibi), kandi rwose ibyo tuvuga ni ukuri"
  15,65,"Bityo, ujyane n’umuryango wawe bujya gucya, unabagende inyuma kandi ntihagire n’umwe muri mwe ureba inyuma (kugira ngo nawe atarimbuka) ndetse mwihute mujye aho mwategetswe"
  15,66,Nuko tumuhishurira iryo tegeko ko kurimburwa kw’abo (banyabyaha) kuri bube kare mu gitondo
  15,67,"Nuko abatuye umujyi (inkozi z’ibibi zo mu mujyi w’i Sodoma) baza bishimye (ku bw’inkuru y’abashyitsi ba Loti, bazi ko bagiye kubakorera ubutinganyi, kuko abo bamalayika bari baje mu ishusho y’abagabo)"
  15,68,"(Loti) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, aba ni abashyitsi banjye; ntimunkoze isoni"
  15,69,"Munatinye Allah,mudatuma ngira ikimwaro"
  15,70,"(Abatuye umujyi) baravuga bati \"Ese ntitwakubujije kwakira abantu (batari muri twe)"
  15,71,"Aravuga ati \"Aba (bakobwa bose bo mu gihugu) ni abakobwa banjye; bityo niba mukeneye gushaka (ngaho nimuze mbabashyingire, aho kwifuza abagabo bagenzi banyu)"
  15,72,"Ndahiriye ku buzima bwawe (yewe Muhamadi)! Mu by’ukuri, (abantu ba Loti) bari mu buyobe bwabo barindagira"
  15,73,Maze urusaku rw’ibihano rubarimbura izuba rirashe
  15,74,Nuko (imijyi yabo) turayubika maze tubanyagiza imvura y’amabuye yo mu muriro
  15,75,"Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bashishoza"
  15,76,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, (iyo mijyi twarimbuye) yari ku nzira nyabagendwa"
  15,77,"Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bemeramana"
  15,78,Ndetse n’abari batuye i Ayikati68 (na bo) bari inkozi z’ibibi
  15,79,"Nuko turabahana. Kandi mu by’ukuri, iyo (mijyi) yombi yari ku nzira nyabagendwa, igaragara"
  15,80,"Kandi rwose, abari batuye Hijiri (na bo) bahinyuye intumwa (Swalehe)"
  15,81,"Twanabahaye ibimenyetso byacu, ariko barabyirengagiza"
  15,82,"Kandi bajyaga bacukura imisozi bagakoramo amazu, (bakayabamo) batekanye"
  15,83,Maze urusaku (rw’ibihano) rubatera mu gitondo cya kare
  15,84,Kandi ibyo bajyaga bakora ntacyo byabamariye
  15,85,"Ntitwanaremye ibirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo bitari ku mpamvu z’ukuri. Kandi mu by’ukuri, imperuka izaza (nta gushidikanya). Bityo (yewe Muhamadi) irengagize amakosa (yabo) ubababarire"
  15,86,"Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe ni we Muremyi, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  15,87,"Kandi rwose (yewe Muhamadi) twaguhaye imirongo (ayat) irindwi (Surat Al Fatihat) isomwa kenshi, tunaguha Qur’an ihambaye"
  15,88,"Ntuzarebeshe amaso yawe (wifuza) ibyo twashimishije by’igihe gito bamwe muri bo (abahakanyi), kandi ntibakagutere agahinda. Kandi ujye wicisha bugufi ku bemera"
  15,89,"Unavuge uti \"Mu by’ukuri, jye ndi umuburizi ugaragara"
  15,90,(Ndababurira ibihano) nk’ibyo (Allah) yahanishije abaciyemo (Qur’an) ibice (bemera bimwe ibindi bakabihakana)
  15,91,Babandi baciye Qur’an mo ibice (bakemera bimwe bagahakana ibindi)
  15,92,"Ndahiye kuri Nyagasani wawe, rwose tuzababaza bose uko bakabaye"
  15,93,"Ku byo bajyaga bakora (bigomeka,babeshya)"
  15,94,"Bityo amamaza ibyo wategetswe, unitandukanye n’ababangikanyamana"
  15,95,"Mu by’ukuri, twe turahagije mu kukurinda abanyagasuzuguro"
  15,96,Babandi babangikanya Allah n’ikigirwamana icyo aricyo cyose. Ariko bazamenya (ingaruka z’ibikorwa byabo)
  15,97,Kandi rwose tuzi ko ubuzwa amahoro n’ibyo bavuga
  15,98,"Bityo, singiza ishimwe rya Nyagasani wawe kandi ube umwe mubamwubamira"
  15,99,"Unagaragire Nyagasani wawe, kugeza ubwo ukuri kukugezeho (urupfu)"